# Shruti Ada Portfolio — Project Context

## Tech Stack
- **Astro 5** static site generator
- **Tailwind CSS 3** for styling (config in `tailwind.config.mjs`)
- **GSAP** for scroll-triggered animations
- **Google Fonts**: Gilda Display (display), PT Serif (body), DM Sans (sans/UI)

## Design System
- Warm cream/beige backgrounds (`cream-100` through `cream-400`)
- Gold/amber accents for buttons, dividers, hover states (`warmgold-300` through `warmgold-700`)
- Charcoal for text (`charcoal-700` through `charcoal-900`)
- Sage green as optional accent (`sage-300` through `sage-800`)

## Architecture
- Single-page portfolio with section-based navigation (#illustrations, #projects, #services, #about, #contact)
- Components are in `src/components/` — each is a self-contained `.astro` file
- Layout (header, footer, nav, loader) is in `src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro`
- All artwork images live in `public/images/portfolio/`
- Image arrays in components define which images appear where

## Key Patterns
- Use Tailwind utility classes (responsive: `md:`, `lg:` prefixes)
- Hover overlays use `.card-hover` and `.card-overlay` classes from `global.css`
- Section dividers use diamond ornaments (`&#x2726;`) with `.section-divider` class
- Buttons use `.btn-primary` or `.btn-outline` classes
- GSAP ScrollTrigger animations are defined in `src/pages/index.astro`

## When Editing
- Keep the warm, elegant aesthetic consistent across changes
- All new images should go in `public/images/` (referenced as `/images/...`)
- When adding sections, wrap in `<section>` with an id for navigation
- Test at mobile (375px), tablet (768px), and desktop (1440px) widths
